Jack Frost;;1998;;PG;;Comedy,Drama,Family;;5.4;;Troy Miller;;Michael Keaton,Kelly Preston,Joseph Cross,Mark Addy,Andrew Lawrence,Eli Marienthal,Will Rothhaar,Mika Boorem,Benjamin Brock,Taylor Handley,Joe Rokicki,Cameron Ferre,Ahmet Zappa,Paul F. Tompkins,Henry Rollins,Dweezil Zappa,Steve Giannelli,Jay Johnston;;Jack Frost is a singer who's on the road most of the time so he can't spend a lot of time with his son Charlie, although they love each other very much. When Jack dies in a car accident, Charlie becomes a very sad young man, until... Jack returns as a snowman! Now they can do all the things they've missed when Jack was human, but what will people think when they see Charlie talking to a snowman and what will happen when the weather gets warmer?;;https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0141109/